tags: every time there's a mispronounced joke
and I don't even care anymore
title: Yes!
body:
Hungary for the win!

Sorry. I haven’t been back home in 2 years and I really miss it sometimes. I literally started clapping and squealing “it’s Hungary, it’s Hungary” when they landed. I click on every geoguessr video thinking it would be awesome if it ended up there, but I never expected it would!

Speaks volume of how little Hungary is mentioned in pop culture that I react this way. And that every time someone makes a Hungary/Hungry joke. (Dan’s lucky he makes me laugh)

I’m going to stop writing now.
